data.description: Beautiful and spacious Holly Hills Charmer is now yours for the taking! This classically styled St. Louis home is just steps away from the park and ideally located near shopping, schools, and Hwy 55 / Loughborough.  At over 2600 sq ft of living space, this one has it all and includes ample room sizes throughout, a separate dining room, an eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, 4 season room, 2 main floor bedrooms on the main and 2 upstairs with a private bathroom, a partially finished lower level with walk-up, large & level fenced yard + a 2 car garage in back. Please make showing requests a minimum of 4 hours in advance (no exceptions as pets need to be removed from home). Offers are to be reviewed as received and require 24-hour response times. We will be reviewing offers for up to 5 days in the event multiple offers are received.
